to open project in intellij ===============
in cmd
cd C:\workspace-intellij\mongodemo
idea64 .


shortcut for open terminal  is atl+F12
short cut for creating non exiting method or class alt + enter

registry short cut ============
Press Ctrl+Shift+A
Search for Registry ...
scroll and find "compiler.automake.allow.when.app.running" then select the checkbox to make it active.
Click close

build project automatically steps===========
File Menu -> settings ...
Expand Build, Execution, Deployment
Select Compiler
Select checkbox Build project automatically
Apply
Click Ok

