ctrl + alt +S   -- open setting options
In the Settings/Preferences dialog Ctrl+Alt+S ,
select Editor | Color Scheme | Color Scheme Font.
Select the Use color scheme font instead of the default checkbox

To navigate to the super method, press Ctrl+U .
To navigate to the implementation, press Ctrl+Alt+B .

alt+ enter  -- short cut for create non existing  method


